name: File organizer template
description:
Use this template for ideas on how to add some structure to your files, or to help communicate document contents with cross functional teams clearly. Use as a file organizer and planner to keep you on track, or as a cover page for your work that encapsulates the contents of your document.


Who's this for?

Professionals and students


What's included?

• File organizer and planner

• Sticker sheet
